{"type":"message","id":"81158379","parentId":"5604a0dc","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:18:46.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The JSON confirms `overall_status: \"ALERT\"`. All checks are failing because the state files are null. This suggests the guard is not finding the state files it expects for today (March 29). This is likely because:\n\n1. Today is Sunday (non-trading day), so most of these scripts didn't run\n2. The state file paths might be dated or expected to have today's data\n\nBut importantly, the `global_market_morning_0850_state.json` exists and shows last_success_at = 2026-03-27. The guard says \"缺少晨报状态文件\" which is strange because the file clearly exists.\n \nThe error message about the missing state file doesn't match what's actually in the JSON—the status is \"OK\" and last_success_at is properly set. This suggests the guard script might be looking for a different state file than the one that exists, or there's a mismatch between what the guard is checking and what's actually there.\n\nThe real issue is likely that today is Sunday, so there's no morning news state file for 2026-03-29, but the script is still trying to validate it. I need to check whether the guard should be skipping validation on weekends or if there's a configuration issue preventing it from finding the existing file at all.","thinkingSignature":"54fd1f934c57fa3ac132b7b60ef86840c769981888b319c38c627c427e2aea74"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nw666g8tyiqp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -100 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27635,"output":308,"cacheRead":23129,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51072,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774750718396,"responseId":"0617befe1f1c20eb24c0a6475fd7f366"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb471998","parentId":"81158379","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:18:47.033Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nw666g8tyiqp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nWORKSPACE = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nREPORT_DIR = WORKSPACE / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nHEALTH_SCRIPT = WORKSPACE / \"scripts\" / \"generate_investment_research_mainline_health.py\"\n\n\ndef today_tag() -> str:\n    return datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n\n\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n\n\ndef run_health() -> tuple[dict[str, Any], Path, Path]:\n    proc = subprocess.run([sys.executable, str(HEALTH_SCRIPT)], cwd=str(WORKSPACE), capture_output=True, text=True, check=True)\n    lines = [line.strip() for line in proc.stdout.splitlines() if line.strip()]\n    md_path = Path(lines[0]) if lines else REPORT_DIR / f\"investment_research_mainline_health_{today_tag()}.md\"\n    json_path = Path(lines[1]) if len(lines) > 1 else REPORT_DIR / f\"investment_research_mainline_health_{today_tag()}.json\"\n    payload = load_json(json_path)\n    return payload, md_path, json_path\n\n\ndef build_summary(payload: dict[str, Any], md_path: Path, json_path: Path) -> str:\n    base = payload.get(\"alert_message\") or \"🩺 量化投研主链巡检：UNKNOWN\"\n    return \"\\n\".join([\n        base,\n        f\"- 健康报告：`{md_path}`\",\n        f\"- 健康JSON：`{json_path}`\",\n    ])\n\n\ndef exit_code(overall: str) -> int:\n    if overall == \"OK\":\n        return 0\n    if overall == \"WARN\":\n        return 10\n    if overall == \"ALERT\":\n        return 20\n    return 30\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    payload, md_path, json_path = run_health()\n    print(build_summary(payload, md_path, json_path))\n    raise SystemExit(exit_code(payload.get(\"overall_status\", \"UNKNOWN\")))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":16,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nWORKSPACE = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nREPORT_DIR = WORKSPACE / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nHEALTH_SCRIPT = WORKSPACE / \"scripts\" / \"generate_investment_research_mainline_health.py\"\n\n\ndef today_tag() -> str:\n    return datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n\n\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n\n\ndef run_health() -> tuple[dict[str, Any], Path, Path]:\n    proc = subprocess.run([sys.executable, str(HEALTH_SCRIPT)], cwd=str(WORKSPACE), capture_output=True, text=True, check=True)\n    lines = [line.strip() for line in proc.stdout.splitlines() if line.strip()]\n    md_path = Path(lines[0]) if lines else REPORT_DIR / f\"investment_research_mainline_health_{today_tag()}.md\"\n    json_path = Path(lines[1]) if len(lines) > 1 else REPORT_DIR / f\"investment_research_mainline_health_{today_tag()}.json\"\n    payload = load_json(json_path)\n    return payload, md_path, json_path\n\n\ndef build_summary(payload: dict[str, Any], md_path: Path, json_path: Path) -> str:\n    base = payload.get(\"alert_message\") or \"🩺 量化投研主链巡检：UNKNOWN\"\n    return \"\\n\".join([\n        base,\n        f\"- 健康报告：`{md_path}`\",\n        f\"- 健康JSON：`{json_path}`\",\n    ])\n\n\ndef exit_code(overall: str) -> int:\n    if overall == \"OK\":\n        return 0\n    if overall == \"WARN\":\n        return 10\n    if overall == \"ALERT\":\n        return 20\n    return 30\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    payload, md_path, json_path = run_health()\n    print(build_summary(payload, md_path, json_path))\n    raise SystemExit(exit_code(payload.get(\"overall_status\", \"UNKNOWN\")))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774750727023}}
